apps.title: ROMEO - Gay Dating & Chat
apps.description:
We’ll spare you a long text, let’s explain in human words who we are. 

To start we are a dating app like so many others. If you’re looking for hot hookups we can help.  Everything you need is here for free without annoying ads.

What makes us special is our community! Most of our users are looking for quality connections, from friendships to real dates. We began as a typical garage start-up with no investors. Today we are based in liberal Amsterdam & Berlin, and we lead ROMEO with the same spirit for more than 20 years.

Thanks for reading


Get the free ROMEO app now and chat with lots of gay, bi, trans, and queer people nearby and worldwide. Create your profile and start chatting within minutes!

10 ROMEO app FREE features you'll LOVE:

- Search for ROMEOs who are online now
- Unlimited free chat
- Customize your profile and share what you are into
- Access search options
- Discover new people in your area
- See who logged in recently
- Hide your real GPS position
- Explore profiles around the world with our travel feature
- Share your private pics for a limited time
- Link and show your friends in your profile

Connect and chat with our Rainbow community.

Are you looking for more features? Upgrade to ROMEO PLUS and make your journey more comfortable, like travelling first class.

 

10 ROMEO PLUS features you'll LOVE:
 

- Unlimited scrolling with more than 120 search options
- Hide profile visits
- Option to 'Appear offline'
- Save unlimited profiles
- Upload unlimited photos
- See your visitors from the last 7 days
- Share private photos with QuickShare
- Choose your grid view and your favorite profile stats
- Appear in your travel destination 2 weeks prior
- Instant messaging! Save frequently used phrases

At ROMEO we want to give you the tools to live your full life and we are one of the largest dating platforms worldwide with more than 3 million gay, bisexual, trans and queer people.

We are proud of developing a gay dating app in a team that is mostly gay and uses ROMEO every day. This is especially meaningful when our community tells us that we stand for more than quick hookups, which means that this can also be a place for more serious relationships and friendship.

We are independent of big companies or advertisement income, that means we can focus on your needs only, on the needs of our community. Furthermore, we believe this down to earth approach is the reason why we have been online since 2001 as GayRomeo and then Planet Romeo .

ROMEO, also known as PlanetRomeo or GayRomeo, is one of the world's most exciting dating apps and social network for gay, bi and trans people. We embrace diversity and support our global Rainbow family.

ROMEO Website version also available.

ROMEO App is for people aged 18 and over.

Download ROMEO App now! 

Gay dating has never been easier. 

Subscription Terms
● Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase.
● Your subscription automatically renews and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
● Any remaining portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited once you purchase an auto-renewing subscription.
● We also encourage you to read our Terms and Privacy below.
● You can manage your subscriptions at any time and auto-renewal can be turned off in your App Store account settings on your device after purchase by going to: Settings » iTunes & App Store » Apple ID » View Apple ID » Subscriptions.

https://romeoapp.com/terms/
https://romeoapp.com/privacy/

apps.title: SweetRing Dating App
apps.description:
“We’ve gathered all the amazing people here, come look for your ideal match!”
“The Top 1 dating app for making real friends and matching with ideal partners in multiple countries.”
 
Welcome to The League, The SweetRing League. This app is not only for those who haven’t made any new friends in the past couple months but also for those who are trying to find their ideal partners. If Tinder is being called the “world’s hottest app” then SweetRing would be “the world’s sweetest app.”
 
You no longer need to be jealous or admire people posting cute pictures with their partners on Instagram or on Facebook. By using SweetRing, you will be able to find the perfect match who watches the same shows as you on Netflix, listens to the same music on Spotify or even criticizes the same celebrities who tweet unbelievable things on Twitter.
 
WHAT MAKES SWEETRING STAND OUT

-    	Over 12 million matches all over the world
SweetRing is available in multiple countries, just like when coffee meets bagel, no matter who you are or where you go, we will do our best and get you the most ideal bagel/coffee for you.

-    	Limited Likes to stimulate sparks
It’s no news that many people are using dating apps to boost their own self-esteem instead of finding love because of the unlimited swipes. After multiple tests and months of research, our team has found the perfect number that will make each and every match of yours meaningful. It might take a while to get used to the idea of having limited likes, but you’ll be surprised by the results.
 
-    	Date Posting Feature
It doesn’t matter if you are looking for a partner to go shopping or even make TikTok videos with. Just post your date request on SweetRing and you’ll be able see who’s down for it. 

-    	Question Posting Feature
Question posting feature allows you to ask questions that are important to you and also, it’s a way to check if you and your matches share the same value. We’ve prepared a bunch of default questions that you can pick from or you can come up with your own! (TIP: You can increase the response rate by 472% if you post interesting questions.) Don’t just swipe left and right when you are using SweetRing, setting up the right questions could be the hinge of your love life.

-    	Buzzing photo
It’s our responsibility to present the best of you to your potential matches. SweetRing has an inclusive photo identifying technology that can decide which picture of you will get more views.
 
-    	Float like a butterfly, sting like a Bumble bee 
Left swipe to dodge, right swipe for like. This is one of the fastest ways to filter out who you are attracted to but do keep in mind that this is not the most effective way to find your ideal match on SweetRing.

 
-    	24/7 security
It’s our job to protect our users in every way possible. When you are using SweetRing all you need to do is to focus on finding your perfect match, leave everything else to us. We’ve got your back!
 
※VIP Premium Options※
Memberships options vary:
7 Days VIP $9.99 (Limited time only!)
30 Days VIP Monthly Subscription $22.99 (~$0.75/Day)
90 Days VIP $64.99 (~$5.40/Week)
180 Days VIP $99.99 (~$4.15/Week)
365 Days VIP $129.99 (~$2.49/Week) *Best Deal*
 
Subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be managed by the user may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase. Prices are in U.S dollars, may vary in countries other than the U.S and are subject to change without notice. Cancellation of the current subscription is not allowed during the active subscription period. SweetRing is a service that provides an avenue for meeting potential partners. We do not guarantee that you will find your future spouse.
 
For further information, please view our Terms and Conditions:
https://www.sweetring.com/rules/rules_terms_of_use.php
https://www.sweetring.com/payment/vip_notice.php

apps.title: Noondate: Dating & Friends
apps.description:
Welcome to Noondate!

Noondate has been providing matching service since 2011

There are thousands of ways to meet people. By the way, why are dating apps all the same? NoonDate's mission is to implement various methods and curiosity of encounters on mobile. The lab has been so hectic today as well.


.No.1 longest usage time among dating app in Korea
.Over 61million accumulated matches

Need someone to talk to when you feel bored or lonely?

Noondate provides free Voice Chat to talk via phone.
There is also an anonymous call feature, so no worrying about exposing yourself to other members.

Want to find someone for blind date by yourself?

Of course it is good to find the ideal type that fits you through acquaintances.
However, you can also find people who share the same appetite with you, for example, newcomers, global friends, who have the same hobby or preference.

How to use?
① Log in with your Facebook account or register an ID with an email account.
② Two profile cards will arrive every day at noon and 8 pm!
③ Select a card to see the person's detail where you can express your interest.
④ If the person likes you, too, congratulations! it's a match!
⑤ If you are willing to start a conversation, you can buy candies and invite the person to chat.

Why NoonDate?
1. Your contact information is kept 100% confidential.
2. Facebook authentication increases credibility of the individuals who may be suggested as your potential match.
3. We carefully review every applicant and only approve those with an appropriate and a completed profile.
4. We do the work for you. No need to bother searching for your ideal type.
5. With more detailed information you provide, our semantic matching algorithm will suggest a better match!

FAQ
Q. How long does it take to get my profile approved?
A. It normally takes 24 hours to process and approve new user profiles as we carefully review all information for any inappropriate content. Users with misleading information may be permanently banned from our service.
Q. Is Facebook account mandatory to create a Noondate profile?
A. No, but Facebook log-in is recommended to fully optimize the service we provide for our users. For instance, logging in with Facebook allows users to avoid being matched with Facebook friends.
Q. Would logging in with Facebook appear on my wall or newsfeed?
A. No, we guarantee your privacy in all circumstances.
Q. I didn't get any cards today.
A. Matches may not be available sometimes depending on your location, interest, and preference settings. Keep your options open to receive cards every day!
Q. How do I get better match suggestions?
A. It depends on the personal information provided by the user. The more and detailed your profile is, the better the match based on your key interests and similarities.

-----
Storage : We are able to store photos and videos that users uploaded on their profile.
Phone : By receiving user's device information, we prevent multiple signup users & misleading use of service.
Location : It is needed when using ""Neighbors"" gps-based matching service.
SMS : It helps users to easily and comfortably continue their signup process.
Microphone : It is needed when using ""Show me your voice"" service.
Camera : It is required for taking photos.

-----
Developer: mozzet
Contact: info.noondate@mozzet.com
We welcome your feedback and suggestions.
* Some features or results may not be available to all users.

Welcome to Noondate!

Noondate has been providing matching service since 2011

There are thousands of ways to meet people. By the way, why are dating apps all the same? NoonDate's mission is to implement various methods and curiosity of encounters on mobile. The lab has been so hectic today as well.


.No.1 longest usage time among dating app in Korea
.Over 61million accumulated matches

Need someone to talk to when you feel bored or lonely?

Noondate provides free Voice Chat to talk via phone.
There is also an anonymous call feature, so no worrying about exposing yourself to other members.

Want to find someone for blind date by yourself?

Of course it is good to find the ideal type that fits you through acquaintances.
However, you can also find people who share the same appetite with you, for example, newcomers, global friends, who have the same hobby or preference.

How to use?
① Log in with your Facebook account or register an ID with an email account.
② Two profile cards will arrive every day at noon and 8 pm!
③ Select a card to see the person's detail where you can express your interest.
④ If the person likes you, too, congratulations! it's a match!
⑤ If you are willing to start a conversation, you can buy candies and invite the person to chat.

Why NoonDate?
1. Your contact information is kept 100% confidential.
2. Facebook authentication increases credibility of the individuals who may be suggested as your potential match.
3. We carefully review every applicant and only approve those with an appropriate and a completed profile.
4. We do the work for you. No need to bother searching for your ideal type.
5. With more detailed information you provide, our semantic matching algorithm will suggest a better match!

FAQ
Q. How long does it take to get my profile approved?
A. It normally takes 24 hours to process and approve new user profiles as we carefully review all information for any inappropriate content. Users with misleading information may be permanently banned from our service.
Q. Is Facebook account mandatory to create a Noondate profile?
A. No, but Facebook log-in is recommended to fully optimize the service we provide for our users. For instance, logging in with Facebook allows users to avoid being matched with Facebook friends.
Q. Would logging in with Facebook appear on my wall or newsfeed?
A. No, we guarantee your privacy in all circumstances.
Q. I didn't get any cards today.
A. Matches may not be available sometimes depending on your location, interest, and preference settings. Keep your options open to receive cards every day!
Q. How do I get better match suggestions?
A. It depends on the personal information provided by the user. The more and detailed your profile is, the better the match based on your key interests and similarities.

apps.title: dua.com - Albanian Dating app
apps.description:
Meet & Date Albanians Worldwide with dua.com - The (only) Albanian Dating App.

Join over 1,000,000 Albanians worldwide on dua.com! 

Whether in Kosovo, Albania, or in Diaspora, connect with Albanians who share your values, traditions, culture, language, and jokes.

WHY CHOOSE DUA.COM?
 - Exclusively for Albanians
 - Verified Profiles: Engage only with real users - verification is now mandatory when you register on dua.com.
 - Spotted Feature: Reconnect with Albanians you've crossed paths with anywhere in the world.
 - Flight Feature: Change your location and meet Albanians in your desired city.
 - Advanced Filters: Find your one love by filtering for important things to you, such as height, religion, language, etc.
 
OUR MISSION
As proud Albanians, our mission is to preserve the Albanian DNA by building strong, healthy families. We are dedicated to protecting our values like Besa, our traditions, and our language, empowering Albanians to reach their full potential.

OUR VISION
BE – Be the one. Be the best version of yourself.
FIND – Find the one. Your one. Your way. (The current app experience)
GROW – Grow together. Supporting couples to build strong, healthy Albanian families.

WHO SHOULD USE DUA.COM?
 - Albanians everywhere seek to find love and build a family with someone who shares their values and culture.

WHAT OUR SUCCESS STORIES SAY

“I wanted someone from my background—an Albanian woman. Regardless of where we live or who we meet, I wanted my life partner to be from Kosovo.” – Edi, Albanian living in Switzerland, married through dua.com.

“I was impressed by how he approached me. It was Eid, and Drilon texted: ‘I’m not sure how to start this conversation, but Happy Eid...’” – Ajshe, Denmark, married through dua.com.

SAFETY IS EXTREMELY IMPORTANT TO US
- 100% Verified Users: Every user must verify their profile during sign-up to ensure a safe community.
- Block Contacts: Block people from your contact list.
- Spotted Control: Add locations where you won’t appear via the Spotted feature.

FOR HER: EXTRA SAFE FEATURES
- Hide My Photos: Choose to hide your photos until you're ready to share them with the public.
- Incognito Mode: Only people you like can see your profile.

DON’T JUST TAKE OUR WORD FOR IT
 - "Çfarë është dua.com - aplikacioni ku përputhen të rinjtë shqiptarë?" - Telegrafi
 - "New App Aims to Connect Albanians around the World" - Balkan Insight
 - "Relationship expert at dua.com, Valon Asani, said…" - Daily Mail
 - "dua.com unites singles with shared cultural values…" - Dating News
 - "dua.com offers matchmaking solutions for meaningful relationships based on shared values." - Daily Star

LOVE BEYOND BORDERS
dua.com makes it easy to connect with Albanians, no matter where you are. Whether you’re dating in New York, Zurich, or Tirana, find people who share your culture and values.

EXPERIENCE DUA PREMIUM
Enhance your experience with dua Premium and enjoy these exclusive features:

 - See Who Liked You: View all your admirers in one place.
 - Unlimited Likes: Explore endless connections with no limits.
 - InstaChats: Send messages before matching.
 - Undo: Reverse your last swipe and give someone a second chance.
 - Flight Feature: Change your location to connect globally.
 - Monthly Boost: Boost your profile to the top for 30 minutes for more visibility.

SUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION
If you choose to purchase dua Premium, payment will be charged to your Apple account. The subscription auto-renews 24 hours before the current period ends. Manage or turn off auto-renewal in your App Store settings anytime. Canceling the current subscription during an active period is not allowed.

You can use dua.com for free without subscribing to dua Premium.

All photos are models, used for illustrative purposes only.

Privacy Policy: https://www.dua.com/privacy-policy

apps.title: Eden AI: Your Dating Coach
apps.description:
EDEN AI - DATING COACH

YOUR FRIEND FOR FINDING LOVE

Dating apps feel stacked against normal guys. You're a great person, but it's hard to show it in a few photos and a short bio. You get lost in the noise.

Eden is your personal coach for dating apps. We're not another app to swipe on. We give you the tools to build a profile that shows who you really are, have better conversations, and date with confidence.

---

A PROFILE THAT ACTUALLY WORKS

It's tough to capture your personality online. Eden helps you pick the right photos and writes a bio that sounds like you—just better. Stop getting overlooked for the wrong reasons and start getting matches who are right for you.

---

NEVER WONDER WHAT TO SAY AGAIN

You matched with someone interesting. Now what? The pressure to be clever is real. Eden reads their profile and gives you openers that actually start a conversation. No more cheesy pickup lines. Just smart, confident messages that lead to real dates.

---

GO ON BETTER DATES

Okay, you got the date. Don't blow it with a boring "drinks?" text. Eden helps you plan creative first dates that are actually fun. Get a step-by-step plan that builds on your conversations and shows you're paying attention.

---

UNDERSTAND YOUR MATCH'S VIBE

Is this conversation going somewhere? Are they actually interested? Stop guessing. Eden looks at how you're both talking and gives you the real story. Understand their personality and if they're into you, so you don't waste your time or energy.

---

LET GO OF THE PAST

Bad breakups can mess with your confidence. It's hard to feel optimistic when you're still thinking about what went wrong. Eden gives you a private space to reflect on your past relationships and learn from them, so you can move on for real and be ready for someone new.

---

BUILD REAL CONFIDENCE

Confidence isn't something you're born with—it's a skill. Our courses teach you the fundamentals of dating in a low-pressure way. Learn how to handle awkward silences or make the first move, so you feel ready for the real thing.

---

SUPPORT AND FEEDBACK

Need Help? Email us at support@getedenai.app.

We Value Your Feedback: Share your thoughts to help us make Eden even better.

---

DOWNLOAD EDEN TODAY AND START DATING ON YOUR OWN TERMS.

apps.title: Veggly – Vegan Dating App
apps.description:
It is so much better to date a person who thinks and eats like you. You can share meals in peace and have a good time, knowing that you agree on such important things as saving the animals, protecting the environment and living a healthy lifestyle. Relationships with non-vegetarians tend to always hit some obstacles that we believe can be avoided altogether, if you find the right vegetarian match. Tired of meeting someone in a restaurant and having to explain where you get your proteins from, or why cows and fishes are living beings just like dogs? Or maybe you simply want to meet like minded people to have a happy conversation or exchange vegan recipes. Either way, that's why we created Veggly! Find, match and chat with vegetarians and vegans near you!

How does Veggly work?
-Find nearby vegan and vegetarian singles for dating
-Mark people you liked (or hide the ones you didn’t)
-Have some real conversations with veggies you matched with using text or audio messages
- We hope you will meet your veg soul mate or at least some good friends

Also:
- Create a profile with your authentic pictures and tell people how long ago you have changed your lifestyle to kickstart a conversation
- Search based on diet, age, distance or scan through profiles who have been online recently
- We are open to different types of vegetarians (raw vegan, keto vegetarian etc.) and gender identities

A few testimonials
- “Our story started when both of us started to scroll through Veggly. Both of us realized that the vegan dating pool is very small and we definitely didn’t expect things to turn out this well. Finding someone who is vegan is great but it obviously takes much more to fall in love and to build a good relationship. From the moment we started talking we realized how many things we have in common and how many shared interests we have.” - Charity and Joe, from Holland and the UK
- “I’ve never had any good experiences with dating apps before but I decided to give Veggly a try. It stood out from the other apps because it was made for the vegan and vegetarian community. It was a much better experience than I could have imagined. I was pleased to see that I already have at least one core value in common with everyone on the app, which is more than what most apps currently have to offer. I’ve met my boyfriend through Veggly so I have them to thank for giving us the chance to meet, for me to fall so hopelessly and madly in love with him. I would definitely recommend Veggly if you are vegan, vegetarian, or plant based. Everyone needs to eat to live and dating is a much better experience when you can agree on something you need to do every day.” - Victoria, from Canada
- “I’ve been a member of the app since the early stages, and in fact, recently I met my current partner through the app!  We clicked right away; we chatted and had video dates for about a month. I was traveling across the country in my self-converted van at that time, and for our first date he drove thousands of miles to meet me in Wyoming, then we traveled for about 5 weeks together!  Crazy story but I think that only happened because we met through this app.” - UX Designer, from San Francisco
- “When I decided to stop eating meat I didn’t know many veg people who I could ask questions to. I decided to download Veggly to chat and look for a veg nutritionist referral (yes, I had that goal hahaha). I ended up meeting a guy who lived 4 blocks from my house, we started talking and we have been together for almost a year now! I never thought I would meet someone nice on a dating app because of my prejudice, but now I’m dating a nice vegan guy!  So the tip of the day is this: download Veggly! Even if you can’t find “the one”, there are plenty of nice people to meet and chat with!” - Chemist, from Brazil

Available for premium users
- Ads-free
- Monthly Super Likes
- Teleportation to any city in the world
- See who liked you
- Reading confirmation

https://www.veggly.net/terms/

apps.title: Muzz: Where Muslims Marry
apps.description:
Muzz is the United States biggest Muslim marriage and social app where Muslims can meet and mingle whether they are looking for marriage or friendship. With over 500,000 Muslim marriages and 500 new couples every day, we know Muzz works. As a Muslim matrimonial app, we’ve included various features to help you meet your perfect Muslim partner in a safe and halal way. Just here to make friends? No problem, we have now launched Muzz Social which is a fun place to post and connect with the community! So, come and say Salams on Muzz.

Muzz is your destination for Muslim marriage, connecting you with 10 million single Muslims. Join a community where 500,000 Muslim marriages have already been celebrated and 500 new couples are formed daily.

On Muzz Social, you can express your thoughts and opinions, whether anonymously or openly. Participate in groups that match your interests and build new friendships. Start engaging with others by greeting them with a warm Salam!

SAFETY FEATURES

Verified Users: In addition to being verified with a selfie, we’ve added an extra layer of security with ID Verification, to make sure you only talk to real single Muslims.

Safety First: We have a dedicated team that is here to help you with your Muslim marriage experience and provide assistance.

Stay Private: You have complete control of who can see your profile and keep your photos private until you're ready to share them.

Chaperone: Need that extra peace of mind? Include a chaperone (or Wali) in your conversations.

WHY MUZZ?

Targeted Filters: Find your perfect match by Location, Interests, Profession, Ethnicity, Language, Education and much more. Explore other cultures, chat with Arabs, South Asian, European Muslims and more.

Video & Voice: Get to know your matches beyond chat with video and voice calling, voice notes and profile videos.

Break The Ice: Let us help you start the conversation. Add three icebreaker questions to your profile, and we’ll reveal your match’s answer once you’ve both connected.

Let Your Personality Shine: Sometimes simply saying Salams or having a brief bio might not fully capture your story. Are you a cat person who loves to visit museums? We’ve added Personality and Interest options to make your profile stand out.

Connect Nationwide : Moved to the city but still looking for a Muslim partner back in your hometown? Use Travel Mode to find Muslims in places such as; California, Texas, Michigan and New York.


HOW IT WORKS
1. Simply sign up and create a profile
2. Use good photos and write a bio letting other single Muslims know what you're looking for
3. We'll show you compatible single Muslims near you who fit your filters and preferences
4. Like them if you're interested, Pass on them if you're not
5. You control who can speak to you. Once you like each other you can start chatting for free
6. Take things to the next level with a voice or video call
7. Complete the other half of your deen and get married!

- ----------------------------------

Use Muzz Gold to accelerate your search. This is available as a weekly, monthly, quarterly, biannual or annual subscription. If you choose to purchase Muzz Gold, payment will be charged to your iTunes account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the iTunes Store after purchase. Prices are in US dollars, may vary in countries other than the US, and are subject to change without notice. No cancellation of current subscriptions is allowed during the active subscription period. If you decide not to purchase Muzz Gold, you can simply continue using Muzz for free.

Privacy https://muzz.com/privacy

Terms https://muzz.com/terms

EULA https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/

apps.title: SURGE – Gay Dating & Chat
apps.description:
SURGE is a gay dating app for gay, bisexual, trans, and queer people to connect. Whether you're looking for a date, relationship, or friendship in the gay community, SURGE gay dating app caters to all your needs! Experience the “SURGE” of meetings with local gay, bisexual, trans, and queer individuals ready for gay romance. 

 Match & Chat for Free
• Browse  – check out gay men nearby by Swiping Right to “like” a guy and Swiping Left to “pass”. 
• Match – swipe right to get matched only with cuties you like. 
• Chat –  if you match with someone, head to the chat section and strike up a conversation immediately for free! Send pics or videos that vanish after a couple of seconds. 
 
 Choose Your Preference
• Filter –  set your preferred age and distance range.
• Secret Pics – show your secret pics after you connect.
• Show Yourself – upload profile pictures and after-match photos to your profile from your photo album, Facebook or Instagram.
• Connect Faster –  send an instant POWER Message to your favorites before you match.

 Security & Privacy
• Profile Verification – see who was verified by our photo verification system.
• App Protection – you can lock your app with a fingerprint.
• Messaging – only users who you match with are able to chat with you.
• Snaps – send pics that disappear after a couple of seconds.
 
 Premium Account Features
• Private Mode – be visible only to the gay men you like or match with.
• Who Liked Me – see everyone interested in you.
• Power Message – send out up to 5 power messages a day so that guy will see your like and message before he swipes left or right on you!
• After-match Gallery – upload pictures that will be only visible to your connections.
• My History – search and edit your previous dislike decision about someone.
• Location Change – modify your location to discover gay men from different cities.
• Hide Age and Distance – hide your age and distance from the users.
• Advanced Filters – modify what type of gay guy you’re looking for or display only verified users.
• Have fun with Stickers – use our custom SURGE stickers in chats.
 
 Premium Membership
• We offer 1 month, 3 months and 12 months options 
• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
• Subscription can be managed by the user and auto-renewal can be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase
  
 About Us
We strive to bring gay men together in a unique gay dating app that will change the way you meet and date other gay men. We’re an open platform where you can be yourself while looking for gay guys. We live by the motto NO LABELS, so it doesn’t matter if you are a Bear, a Twink, a Jock or a Show Queen. Come for fun and search through thousands of profile pics to find your perfect guy. Try SURGE gay dating app and change the way you approach new gay men.
 
Terms of Use
• Inappropriate or explicit photos are strictly prohibited. Any publicly exposed inappropriate content will be removed. You must be at least 18 years old to sign up for SURGE gay dating app.

 Contact Us
• 24/7 Admin Support: We are here to help and we speak your language. Message our admin and we will get back to you as soon as possible.
• Feedback: Any recommendation or comment? We value your opinion, let’s make our platform a better place together.

Check our Privacy Policy for more information:
http://www.surgeapp.co/privacy
http://www.surgeapp.com/terms

Follow us on Social Media to connect with Surge gay community:
Facebook @surgeapp.co
Instagram @surgeapp

apps.title: EME Hive - Dating, Go Live
apps.description:
East Meet East has been rebranded to EME Hive!
 
With over 1 million users, EME Hive is a lit dating and live-streaming app for meeting new people and joining like-minded communities around you. Whether you are looking for serious dating, seeking a relationship, flirting with other singles, or video chatting with our mixed community, we’ve got you covered!
 
How do we have so many successful matches?
1. Unique Filters - Whether you are looking to connect with Asians - Korean, Vietnamese, Chinese, Filipino, Japanese - or with Hispanics, African-Americans, Mixed individuals, or Caucasians, our proprietary filter options will help you find that perfect cupid match.
2. With a single tap you can:
     - Chat, flirt, and start dating with new singles nearby
     - Discover who liked you
     - Match with people just like you, thanks to our score algorithm
     - Receive 1-to-1 match recommendations
     - Watch a live stream, or go live yourself
 
Make your profile shine with your best pictures and showcase your unique personality by including a little something about yourself to increase your match potential. Smile at someone. If someone smiles back, it’s a match! Download the app to get matched with a compatible cupid, go on a date, and get into the meaningful relationship you have been looking for!
 
Not ready to start dating again or taking a break? Join our live-stream communities to connect with people in your cultural heritage, form your Asian squad, showcase your talent, or seek out new friends from all around the world. It’s fun, positive, and free! EME Hive is a new way to experience social interactions. Say no to FOMO and live in the moment today!
 
* Go Live - Cook? Sing? Dance? Flirt? Showcase your hidden talents. Gain fans and admirers, receive gifts, make friends, and form your squad.
 
* Watch Livestream - Daily events with an active community. Watch and be entertained by talented broadcasters such as Truth Or Dare or the Bachelor Show. Your new addiction has arrived.
 
* Video Chat & Live Chat - Go live together with others in a group video chat with up to 4 people in a live chat room. Cure boredom while you stay at home. Speak up about social issues. Talk about the latest gear. Watch a movie together. Virtual date with your Cupid match. Put your voice out there and be a thought leader today.
 
* VLOG - Share your life, be inspired with fresh ideas, or practice a new language from different Asian and minority cultures such as Korean, Japanese, Chinese, Vietnamese, Filipino, or Spanish, and become a better human being.
 
Formerly known as EastMeetEast, EME Hive is a unique mixed space for dating, live chat, and community building. Go live to video chat, meet new people around you, discover your Hive, and bond together.
 
Try the EME Hive app today, and live in the moment. Go live, make friendships, date, or seek out a meaningful relationship and bring positive social energy in your creative way.
 
Your feedback helps us improve EME Hive, please contact us at hello@emehive.co
View our Privacy Policy: http://www.emehive.co/help/privacy
View our Terms of Service: http://www.emehive.co/help/tos

With 15 years in the dating industry, 10 million users, and being 100% FREE, it’s no wonder that Adam4dam Radar is the industry-leading gay social network. Whether you’re looking for a date, chat, friends, long term relationships, networking opportunities or casual fun, you’ll find it on Adam4Adam Radar. We’ve been part of our users’ lives for so long that they’ve even given us a nickname — A4A. What other app can say the same?

Browse. Chat. Meet. It is easy to meet guys on Adam4Adam and we redesigned our app to make it even better, faster, and easier to use. We’re the only app offering a full, FREE experience with tons of features that other apps charge for.

- Browse unlimited profiles in five different grids based on your location
- Browse users in other cities if you plan to travel
- View all users or only users that are online
- Use over 20 filters—age, body type, preferences, etc.—to find what you’re looking for
- Send unlimited photos within a conversation  
- Send and receive unlimited messages 
- Send saved phrases to speed things up
- Add users to your favorites and block others
- See who favorited you
- Send your location within a conversation
- Make the first move and send a smile to users that you appreciate
- Customize your profile to represent who you are
- Connect your social media with your profile
- Upload multiple photos in your profile
- Drag and drop your photos to sort them
- Hide your last visit to a profile
- Track who visited your profile
- Show your travel plans with the Plan-a-Trip feature

Adam4Adam is free to download and use. However, we also offer a VIP membership subcription valid for 7 days, 30 days, 90 days, 180 days or 1 year that offers these extra features:

- Turn off publicity
- Browse discreetly using the invisible mode
- Get listed in the Featured Members grid
- Keep unlimited conversation history
- Save up to 200 conversations
- Upload more photos in your profile
- Get unlimited favorites and blocks
- Get priority support and skip ahead of the queue

If you choose to purchase Adam4Adam VIP, payment will be charged to your iTunes account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period at the same price. Subscriptions may be managed by the you at any time and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the your iTunes account settings after purchase. QuackQuack is the best matchmaking and dating app to meet, chat, flirt and date eligible, verified and like-minded singles. QuackQuack is the only online dating app in India where we match you with singles from your city, age group and interests. QuackQuack has 39 million registered users and you will surely find your date with us.

Here is what you can do with the QuackQuack app:
Create your profile free, add photos and go browsing thousands of matches in your city. You can see matches who belong to your age group and city. If you like anyone, simply just express interest by click of a button. If they like you too, it’s a match! Once matched, you can chat on QuackQuack with each other and setup your date and mingle offline!

All profiles are screened and verified by our moderators to ensure you match with genuine and verified singles only. All users have to verify their mobile numbers, so you can be sure that you’d be dating only genuine and verified singles. We are not a casual dating app nor a hookup app, all users on our desktop and mobile app are genuine singles looking for love. All your information and photos are safe as we have strong back-end moderation and you will have a clean experience unlike other unsafe dating apps that do not moderate content.

QuackQuack has majority of local users from major cities in India. So, don’t worry, we’ve got your back in finding a match. So, stop reading further and download the QuackQuack app and join 39 million singles and go dating... Who knows, you might as well get on the aisle with your match...Woo hoo!

The app is free to download and use. We also offer an optional subscription package.The packages currently cost at Rs. 990 for 1 month, 2500 for 3 months, Rs. 4300 for 6 months and Rs. 6900 for 12 months.

Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. You cannot cancel the current subscription during the active subscription period.

apps.description:
Are you tired of being nagged by your relatives about your dating life? Do you want to find someone who shares your South Asian culture and values? If so, you need Vinita - the new name in town for South Asian dating.

HOW WE WORK OUR MAGIC
In the desi community especially, singles are often criticized by relatives and parents. Vinita is on a mission to put your dating life back into your own hands! Our app enables you to take up the driver's seat.

* We’re a ‘smart’ app... meaning the more you swipe, the better we can understand what you’re into.

* Our interface is designed to grant you a flawless swiping experience so you can focus on the choice at hand.

* Our profile features allow you to recognize potential attributes fast with every swipe. We’re free to download & use!

MESSAGE FROM OUR FOUNDER
“Welcome to Vinita, the dating app that celebrates your South Asian heritage and helps you find your perfect match. Vinita is named after my beloved aunty, who was always eager to arrange dates for me with eligible singles. She inspired me to create this app, where you can connect with people who share your culture, values, and preferences. Vinita is more than just a dating app, it’s a community of South Asians who are looking for relationships in all forms.”

apps.description:
Tired of getting left-swiped on dating apps?  
A standout profile picture is key to getting RIGHT swipes on dating apps! That’s where Rz.AI(Former name: RizzGPT) comes in – the ultimate tool to upgrade your pictures and help you win over your crush. With just ONE great picture, you could skyrocket your chances of landing 100 matches! Click, generate, and score!

Profile Max analyzes your selfie, offering tailored styles like classy, rugged, or outdoor – all without making you look unrealistic or catfished. You’ll still be you, but an even more captivating version. With Profile Max, you’ll stand out in a crowded dating world. Please note: We do not offer medical advice. All recommendations should be viewed as suggestions. Always check with a professional and do your own research before making any changes.

Struggling to reply or break the ice when it counts?
With Rz.ai, simply upload your chat screenshots — whether it's a tough question or a tricky conversation — with just one click, our AI will craft the perfect response. You can also choose from flirty jokes, cheesy pickup lines, or even input your own custom topics. Whatever the scenario, we generate replies that impress and keep the conversation going.

Rz.ai Keyboard - one tap away from being a RizzGod
If you want to instantly reply and break the ice on other dating apps without the hassle of switching between apps, try the Rz.ai Keyboard. You’ll get the best messages instantly, with no delay.

Versatility for Every Occasion  
Rz.ai goes beyond dating – whether you’re navigating a romantic connection, networking, or professional chats, our algorithm generates authentic and engaging responses for any situation. It’s more than just a dating wingman – it’s your go-to communication ace. Rz.ai works seamlessly with all major dating and social apps, including Tinder, Grindr, Hinge, Bumble, POF, Badoo, Wizz, WooPlus, Snapchat, Facebook, and Instagram etc...

apps.title: Jigsaw® Dating
apps.description:
A new dating experience for people ready to find a relationship.

Relationships are formed in real life and we're here to make that journey as exciting as possible.

We provide the best online and offline dating experience by hosting a variety of events across the US every month and our app is the ultimate companion to make it happen. We're constantly expanding to add more cities and different event styles, giving you the freedom to choose what works best for you.

With your membership, you unlock unlimited access to our monthly singles events and you'll get to connect in the app after you've met! Plus, enjoy exclusive event perks (like flexible tickets, access to exclusive members-only presales, and more!)

At Jigsaw Dating, we're all about providing you with the smoothest, most enjoyable dating experience.

If you're dedicated to finding your missing piece, you're at the right place.

MONTHLY SINGLES EVENTS

Our variety of dating events are curated to help you connect in spaces that suit you best. Our collection of events range from mixer-style happy hours and cozy coffee shop speed dates, to singles pickleball, arcade night, and more. We have over 100 events per month in major cities across the US and each has a dedicated host to kickstart the fun. Members get more, but our events are open to everyone with a ticket!

OFFLINE AND ONLINE CONVERSATIONS

Missed a connection or want to meet more people? We’ve got you. Spark a new connection or keep the conversation going after the event with the safety and comfort of the app! Everyone in the app is fully verified to ensure no bots or scammers, powered by Yoti, our security partner. Online, you’ll meet other genuine singles who are committed to finding a real-life relationship, in your own time. Every day, you'll receive matches selected based on compatibility with other
singles in your area.

LEARN MORE ABOUT YOURSELF

Jigsaw Dating understands that meeting in person can sometimes feel a bit daunting. That's why Jigsaw Dating has designed tailored in-app sessions just for you. Starting with an introductory session designed to understand where you are in your dating journey, Jigsaw Dating customizes your experience and supports you in reaching your dating goals. Members get more with curated dating sessions, content, and coaching tips, all designed to help you boost your confidence and find a healthy relationship.

DEDICATED SUPPORT

The Jigsaw team is dedicated to helping you find your missing piece, so don’t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions or ideas! Our entire dating experience has been designed with our members' feedback at the forefront of each feature, event, and offering. The Jigsaw team can be found on email or messenger anytime and at the events you will be welcomed each time by our dedicated team of hosts.

SUBSCRIPTION INFO

Payments to join our community will be charged to your Apple ID account when your purchase is confirmed. Your subscription automatically renews unless you've turned off auto-renew at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period; you can manage your subscription settings and turn off auto-renewal by going to the subscriptions section of your Apple ID account.

Support: support@jigsaw.co

Terms of Service: https://jigsaw.co/us-terms

Privacy Policy: https://jigsaw.co/us-privacy

PIECE & LOVE xoxo

apps.title: Meetup: Social Events & Groups
apps.description:
Pursue your interests with people who share them, both online and in person. With over 60 million members, Meetup helps you build a career network, discover a tech community, create a personal brand, make time for your hobbies, and meet friends who share similar interests. 

Easily meet people you know you’ll get along with and create groups of friends that will be as excited as you to embrace your hobbies, participate in online or local events or engage in discussions. Download the Meetup app and host your own events or join one of the 100,000 Meetup events with new people happening every week. 

Discover local and online events

Meet new people and get matched with over 330,000 groups and friends based on your network of interests, from tech conferences to free yoga and everything in-between
Explore online or local events by category, search by keyword, or see what’s popular in your area with a map
Save events you’re interested in and come back to  them later. Pick and choose the people and friends you want to meet at all the events that you like
Have discussions with the people you meet and use direct messaging to stay in touch with your new friends
Meet  people who are interested in the same local or online events, create new groups of friends and expand your online network

Start a group

Host your own events online and in person by creating a group on your favorite topic, and meet friends who wants to participate
Watch your community of friends and network of people grow as your group is recommended to interested people and potential new friends to meet
Easily personalize and schedule events on-the-go, and manage your group from anywhere
Keep the momentum going between events by sharing photos and using discussions and instant messaging to connect with the people and friends in your group that you are keen to meet

Get in touch with questions or suggestions: iossupport@meetup.com

In order to recommend Meetup events that are hosted by local groups, we use your device's precise location (GPS and network-based).

apps.description:

Ahlam was developed with great love and attention to details. Our team has more than 10 years of experience in dating sites and we tried to combine most important features without overloading. If you are looking for USA arab dating, UK arab chat, arabs in Canada, Europe, GCC and other arab countries you came to right place. Please send us feedback, questions, ideas to support@ahlam.net

بخبرتنا التي فاقت 10 سنوات في مواقع التعارف، جمعنا لكم أهم المميزات الفعالة .
اذا كنت تبحث عن تعارف للعرب، دردشه بالعربي، للحب والصداقة والعثور على شريك مناسب للزواج - نحن في "Ahlam" يمكننا مساعدتك كما ساعدنا بالفعل الاف المستخدمين السعداء الذين وجدوا الشريك المناسب لهم عن طريق تطبيقنا. (يمكنك ان تجد بعض التعليقات في https://ahlam.net/testimonials) 

الميزات الرئيسية: 
- تتم مراجعة جميع الصور والنصوص يدويا من قبل المدقيقين لدينا بحيث تكون قاعدة البيانات ذات جودة عالية
- يمكن الإبلاغ عن اي إسائة من قبل المشتركين بسهولة  (عن طريق النقر على "شكوى" في حساب المشترك)
- يمكن حظر المشتركين في حالة الإساءة بسهولة (بالنقر على "حظر" في حساب المشترك)
- التسجيل الفوري  والدخول عبر الشبكات الاجتماعية (لا يتم نشر اي معلومات)
- توثيق الحسابات في 4 خطوات: صور شخصية، بريد الكتروني، شبكات التواصل الاجتماعي، رقم الهاتف. يتم تمييز الحسابات التي تم التحقق منها بشارة خاصة وتحظى بالأولوية. نوصيك بتوثيق الحساب (مجانًا) بعد تحميل التطبيق مباشرةً
-  تحميل ما يصل إلى 30 صورة بجودة عالية وتغيير ترتيب الصور
-  يمكن للمرأة الحفاظ على إخفاء الهوية واختيار واحد من الصور الرمزية الجميلة التي تعكس شخصيتها 
- البحث عن أشخاص قريبة منك (الموقع الجغرافي) مع خيار لتحديد مسافة البحث
- البحث بنقرة واحدة فقط عن المعايير المهمة مثل: الصور، الشهادات، مع / بدون أطفال
- "لعبة معجب او غير معجب" - تطابق سريع بالصور.  مشاهدة الصور, اختيار معجب أو غير معجب - سيتم إخطار كلا الجانبين في حالة الاعجاب المتبادل
- تصفية نتائج البحث لرؤية المستخدمين الفعالين فقط (من سجل الدخول في آخر يومين)
- تصفية نتائج البحث لرؤية المستخدمين المتصلين الآن
-  انقر "أعجبني"   لإظهار اهتمامك بمستخدمين آخرين 
-  نقرة واحدة لتغيير إعدادات الرسائل الواردة ، لقطع وصول الرسائل الغير مرغوب بها


إذا كانت لديك أسئلة / شكاوى بخصوص التطبيق، يرجى إرسال رسالةبالبريد الإلكتروني إلى support@ahlam.net وسنقوم بالرد عليك في اقرب وقت. يمكنك أيضًا تفحص الأسئلة الشائعة على موقعنا https://ahlam.net/support والاتصال بنا من خلال الدردشة المباشرة أو نموذج الاتصال هنا https://ahlam.net/contact

- يتم  تجديد العضوية تلقائيا حتى تقوم بإلغائها. يمكنك الإلغاء حتى 24 ساعة قبل انتهاء العضوية الحالية
- بعد شراء العضوية ، ستتمكن من التحكم بها وإلغاءها في إعداداتك
- يتم الاحتفاظ بجميع البيانات الشخصية وفقًا لسياسة الخصوصية في Ahlam.net. للمزيد من المعلومات:

apps.title: Are We Dating The Same Guy?
apps.description:
This app was created to be a safe place for women to support and empower other women by sharing information to protect each other from men who might exhibit any type of toxic or dangerous behavior.

This space can also be used to inquire about someone you're dating or may potentially date to see if anyone has had any experiences with them and give other women the chance to share relevant information.

This is also a welcoming space where women can ask for advice and relationship support, as well as post stories, memes, or anything else dating related that can help bring us together, keep us safe, or help us feel less alone.

Features of the AWDTSG app include:

-Screenshot & Screen-Record Blocking: The app prevents other users from taking screenshots or screen recordings of anything posted within the app, and creates logs of anyone who ever attempts to screenshot a post. We even block text from being copied out of the app. We’re always adding more features to do everything we can to keep your story private and safe.

-Anonymous Posting & Commenting: Feel free to post anonymously and know that your identity is safe with us. You can also comment anonymously on any post, with a uniquely generated name that is different for every single post!

-Verified Women: We make sure every person requesting was manually checked and confirmed to be a real woman by one of our volunteers.

-Stay Safe Wherever You Go: The app allows you to see and share information in multiple different cities, all in one place.

Features of the AWDTSG app include:
